summary: An Ordinance providing for the purchase of certain portions of the east one half (E 1/2) of the northeast one-fourth (NE 1/4) of the Northwest one fourth (NW 1/4) of Section Two (2) Township Twenty-three (23) North Range Four (4) East W. M. for park and playground purposes for a sum not to exceed Eight Thousand Dollars ($8,000.00) payment to be made from the Park Fund of the City of Seattle.
